 of this, wanted to post it here too :) I did paint Jack about 7 years ago. But wanted to repaint it. I did a stupid thing back then and a company asked for the rights to the video for promises of exposure! (Very dumb, I know, but I didn't know better at the time.) Decided to repaint it and try to improve it as much as possible so I could have it back for myself :)

Thanks to the people who are super kind and not inappropriate on my posts, it's appreciated.

Faq: 
I use body paint and do these in a mirror
It's from The Nightmare Before Christmas
No, it is not AI.
I use professional body paint covers 
I paint these by looking in a mirror 
It takes between 6-10 hours each
Body painting myself is my hobby/passion
I do own clothes
If you want to see more I am MCroft07 on IG, twitter, Tiktok, YouTube
I paint them live on twitch
I desaturated the video a little bit at the end so it wasn't so jarring when I had my mouth open for the lip syncs and it was bright pink
I like doing the lip syncs, they're fun for me while I paint them
The reason why there is a disconnect between the head and the neck is purposeful. I have had to create a "round" head and used the maximum width possible for my own head to make the illusion work. If I paint an extended neck it will look wrong when my head is turned. It's fine anyway, I pretend it's a shadow, and alsohe can remove his own head in the film.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4r2NjCl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MCroft07]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I love it and yet it feels like we have to defend it.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xJKEDJn</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4Zf7zOf.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I specifically told him to not get anything expensive, to not get something flashy and to not get something that is irreplaceable. 

AND YET, people are judging him (even though they try to twist into curiosity). Its tearing him down and its making him feel bad.

But I didnt want him to spend alot of money. We arent in that position financially and I hardly wear any jewelry. I also lose shit way too easily for something expensive</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xJKEDJn</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SpriteandCats]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Progress!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4zavL0W</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/544KJl3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>June 2023</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MFz7H0r.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>May 2024</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IejIAaD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Aug 2024</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4zavL0W</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sammyCosmosCat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Good afternoon</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7f9Fq5V</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dubxclt.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xgd6yMi.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Vp9KZXz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C6oOhSA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uO0v0Kn.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mXQHOZI.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RxHr9lx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tiswxXk.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></